      <title>Hexo套用NextT</title>
      <link href="/2019/09/11/Hexo%E5%A5%97%E7%94%A8NextT/"/>
      <url>/2019/09/11/Hexo%E5%A5%97%E7%94%A8NextT/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>安裝NextT後, \Blog\themes下出現next資料夾</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> \blog</span><br><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>hexo預設使用的themes是landscape,修改blog配置文件_config.yml<br>2.1 搜尋並修改 theme: next 即可啟用</p></li><li><p>主題設定有三種模式, Muse、Mist、Pisces、Gemini, 本Blog是採用Gemini<br>3.1 修改themes的配置文件_config.yml<br>scheme: Gemini</p></li><li><p>語言設置:修改blog配置文件_config.yml<br>4.1 language: zh-tw</p></li></ol><p>References <a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NexT 使用文档</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
            <tag> NextT </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>用Hexo建立Blog</title>
      <link href="/2019/09/11/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8BBlog/"/>
      <url>/2019/09/11/%E7%94%A8Hexo%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8BBlog/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>Hexo事前安裝準備:node.js + Git。</p></li><li><p>登入GitHub帳號並新增一個repository且Repository name 必須命名為 UserName + “.github.io”。</p></li><li><p>使用Git Bash開啟指令視窗並輸入以下指令來獲得ssh-rsa key。</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git config --global user.name <span class="string">"github UserName"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global user.email <span class="string">"github email"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"github email"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.1接下來詢問都按Enter略過</p></li><li><p>從ssh key文件預設位置 C:\Users\用戶名.ssh下，找到id_rsa.pub文件(文件內全都是key的一部分)。</p></li><li><p>在GitHub -&gt; Setting -&gt; SSH and GPG keys，新增SSH keys<br>5.1 Title任意取即可。<br>5.2 key填入id_rsa.pub文件內所有內容。</p></li><li><p>確認node.js 是否安裝成功</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>新增hexo blog資料夾，cmd -&gt; cd至資料夾 -&gt; 安裝hexo</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>初始化blog</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">8.1 hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>cd 至資料夾\blog</p></li><li><p>新增新文章<br>10.1 hexo new my_first_post</p></li><li><p>產生靜態檔案<br>啟動local server , default port 4000</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更換port</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server -p 5000 來更換port</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p>12.在\blog下找到配置文件_config.yml<br>13.1 修改deploy配置<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">repository: http://github.com/用戶名/用戶名.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>13.部署至GitHub<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>13.1 hexo d (這步如有出現ERROR Deployer not found: git錯誤),在\blog下安裝<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>14.在browser輸入 “UserName”.github.io 即可看到Blog</p><p>References <a href="https://junyou.tw/hexo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">使用 Hexo 在 Github 建立部落格</a><br>References <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_21808961/article/details/84476504" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo d命令报错 ERROR Deployer not found: git</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
